channel.title: JayXat - Evolution 3.0
channel.description:
Good day to all!
JayXat is finally back after months of thinking, bragging and development.
We've had help from many people, suggestions by many. And all that has hopefully paid off.
We don't aim to compete with other Xat Private Servers, or spam others. We want to have a clean kick-off and if it ever comes a clean end.
All users who register today get free 10k iXats, and users who register in the next hour get member in Lobby chat.
We will be looking for staff members to moderate the Lobby as it progresses.
http://jayxat.user32.com
Thanks for reading!
I would also like to thank;
-Legendfoxy, I've been bugging him like a bee. He's helped so much, and I would love to do atleast this for him.
